PN,46502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1777551071
OL,3,CFormer police officer barred for using
OL,4,Cracist and sexist language while on
OL,5,Cduty
OL,7,FThe investigation launched by Gwent
OL,8,FPolice's Professional Standards
OL,9,FDepartment (PSD) in June 2025 related
OL,10,Fto three allegations that Tancock
OL,11,Fbreached the professional standards of
OL,12,Fbehaviour.
OL,14,FAssistant Chief Constable Nick McLain
OL,15,Fchaired the accelerated misconduct
OL,16,Fhearing and said: "The behaviour of
OL,17,Fthis former officer was totally
OL,18,Funacceptable; neither we nor the
OL,19,Fpublic accept such conduct from police
OL,20,Fofficers whether on or off duty.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1777551071
OL,3,CFormer police officer barred for using
OL,4,Cracist and sexist language while on
OL,5,Cduty
OL,7,F"Our communities rightfully expect our
OL,8,Fofficers and staff to uphold the
OL,9,Fhighest standards of behaviour and not
OL,10,Fconduct themselves in a way which will
OL,11,Fcause public trust and confidence in
OL,12,Fthe service to be undermined. However,
OL,13,Fthis former officer has failed to do
OL,14,Fso.
OL,16,F"We will not accept misogyny, racism
OL,17,For discrimination from our officers or
OL,18,Fstaff.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
