PN,46504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1777551071
OL,3,CFormer police officer barred for using
OL,4,Cracist and sexist language while on
OL,5,Cduty
OL,7,F"The vast majority of the police
OL,8,Fofficers, staff and volunteers, who
OL,9,Fwork for Gwent Police conduct
OL,10,Fthemselves impeccably and work
OL,11,Ftirelessly to protect the public,
OL,12,Fthose very few who choose to breach
OL,13,Fthe standards expected of them
OL,14,Fundermine the public's trust in
OL,15,Fpolicing."
OL,17,FFormer police constable Tancock will
OL,18,Fnow be placed on the College of
OL,19,FPolicing's barred list.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@JO]
